<center>
<a href="/lead-inst/tour.html.cgi">Next Stop On The Tour</a> <p>
This is page 9 out of 26.<p>




</center>
<p>
<html>
<head>
<title>Americans for Tax Reform</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor =#ffffff>
