 <P>
<h4> With over 40,000 members nationwide, the Small Business Survival Committee (SBSC) is the fastest
 growing small business advocacy group in the nation.  SBSC is a nonpartisan, nonprofit free-market o
rganization that works to roll back the burdensome tax and regulatory demands on business and entrepr
eneurs.
</h4>
