http://www.conservative.org:80/sbsc/tax-0995.html 204.71.237.88 19970208121621 text/html 5239
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 12:17:06 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:53 GMT
