<li>See Ralph Keeney, "Mortality Risk Induced by Economic Expenditure," <I>Risk Analysis</I>, Vol. 10, No. 1 (1990); letter from James MacRae, Acting Administrator and Deputy Administrator, Office of Information and Regulatory Affairs, Office of Management and Budget, to Nancy Risque-Rorbach, Assistant Secretary for Policy, Department of Labor (DOL), March 10, 1992.<p>
