<i>In addition, six donors wish to remain anonymous</i>
<p>
</CENTER>

A copy of The Heritage Foundation's audited financial report is available upon 
request.
<p>
<a href="/heritage/dept_writeups/mbrship.html">Join the Heritage Foundation!</a>
