<a name=feedback>
<center><h2>Feedback</h2></center>
<b>"The whole country has been calling about your segment all week! I couldn't believe the nerve you hit. You are fabulous. Come on again every time you have a report. You're the best, and the only way we can break through."
<p>
-- a note from Mary Matalin to Brent Bozell, after he guested on the premiere of her radio talk show.</b>
