<TITLE>Midge Decter -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>Midge Decter</H3>
<HR>
<B>TRUSTEE</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/decter.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>Decter is an author and editor whose essays, reviews, and social criticism have appeared in numerous periodicals during the past two decades. Her books include <i>The New Chastity</i> and <i>Liberal Parents, Radical Children</i>. She has worked for <i>Commentary</i>, <i>Harper's</i>, <i>Saturday Review</i>, and Basic Books.</P>

