http://www.conservative.org:80/empower/benn0116.html 204.71.237.88 19970208191617 text/html 5614
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 19:17:00 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:55:00 GMT
